            <title><![CDATA[呼和浩特市以外车辆及司乘人员11日起禁止入呼]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>中国内蒙古</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>自治区</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>呼和浩特市冠病疫情严峻，当地发布通告，将</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>禁止呼和浩特市以外的车辆及司乘人员进入呼和浩特市。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据央视新闻报道，呼和浩特市应对新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情防控工作指挥部</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>星期一（</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>10月10日）发布通告称，为进一步防范疫情通过公路交通传播扩散，最大限度降低疫情外溢和输入风险，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>从星期二（10月11日）零时起，呼和浩特市以外的车辆及司乘人员原则上禁止进入呼和浩特市。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>公告要求，居住地在呼和浩特市的居民，待疫情形势平稳后有序返回。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>公告也要求，途经呼和浩特市的车辆需绕行。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>所有货车及司乘人员入呼须严格落实测温、扫青城码、查验48小时内一次核酸检测阴性证明等措施，一律进行落地核酸采样，即采即走即追。入呼后，点对点闭环运输，货车司乘人员全程不下车、不接触，货物即装（卸）即走，在市域内不得随意停靠。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>截止星期天（</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>10月9日</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>）24时，呼和浩特市新增本土确诊病例87例，新增无症状感染者499例。呼和浩特市本土确诊病例794例，无症状感染者2538例。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<div id="innity-in-post"></div>
<div id="dfp-ad-midarticlespecial">
        
</div>



<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>呼和浩特市于</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>10月</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>2日暂停多类公共场所运营。呼和浩特市</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>10月</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>7日召开疫情防控工作新闻发布会称，国庆节假期后将继续加强对社会面的管控，中小学生继续进行居家生活和线上学习。同日，呼和浩特市委宣传部发布通告要求在呼人员原则上暂不离呼。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      


